      "id": "PopularPost38739",
      "post_content": "Adding to Kurhan:  \n  \nNot to mention after you play a spell, your opponent gains priority to respond to it, during which you have to let him or her play anything they want to (if they can) before you can put another spell on the stack.  \n  \nBut yeah, killer card. Too situational in my opinion, but i smell a silly combo with [Isochron Scepter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Isochron Scepter) with this, and [Panoptic Mirror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Panoptic Mirror) with a [Last Chance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Last Chance). Heheheh..., oh pointless combos, how fun you all are.",
