    {
      "id": "PopularPost285009",
      "post_content": "[Ad Nauseam](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Nauseam) does **NOT** work with this card. It causes life loss which [Angel's Grace](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace) does NOT stop.  \nThe rulings read: \"The last sentence applies only if your life total is being reduced by **damage**. Other effects or costs (such as 'lose 1 life' or 'pay 1 life') can reduce your life total below 1 as normal.\" Thus your life would be reduced below zero if you [Ad Nauseam](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Nauseam) into a card with a higher CMC than you have life.  \n  \nAlso, this card doesn't completely make you unkillable, you still lose the game if you have 10+ poison counters or less than 0 life at the end of your turn.  \n  \nAs others have stated, this does not end the stack either. Spells and abilities below it on the stack can be responded to or countered as soon as this finishes resolving. Split Second only prevents players from casting spells or activating abilities until the spell with it leaves the stack. Triggered abilities still can trigger and resolve before a... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Suigen_Yukiouji",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost285009\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ad Nauseam\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Nauseam\">Ad Nauseam</a> does <b>NOT</b> work with this card. It causes life loss which <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Angel's Grace\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Angel's Grace\">Angel's Grace</a> does NOT stop.<br/>The rulings read: \"The last sentence applies only if your life total is being reduced by <b>damage</b>. Other effects or costs (such as 'lose 1 life' or 'pay 1 life') can reduce your life total below 1 as normal.\" Thus your life would be reduced below zero if you <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ad Nauseam\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ad Nauseam\">Ad Nauseam</a> into a card with a higher CMC than you have life.<br/><br/>Also, this card doesn't completely make you unkillable, you still lose the game if you have 10+ poison counters or less than 0 life at the end of your turn.<br/><br/>As others have stated, this does not end the stack either. Spells and abilities below it on the stack can be responded to or countered as soon as this finishes resolving. Split Second only prevents players from casting spells or activating abilities until the spell with it leaves the stack. Triggered abilities still can trigger and resolve before a... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 285009)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '285009'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy90930\">Suigen_Yukiouji</span>\r\n                                (12/8/2012 8:00:45 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
